pkg bus_handle v1
  desc "Bus message keys strip a Handle* prefix (DDD application-service convention)"
  author "VEIL"

  bus_policy
    strip_name_prefix Handle

  prompt
    Bus naming pack (bus_handle):
    - Handler HandleCreateUser publishes bus type CreateUser (prefix stripped).
    - Disable in product: veil.toml [codegen] bus_strip_prefix = "none"
    - Different prefix: bus_strip_prefix = "Cmd" or a forked layer.
